<C>__{delaney}
<D>__{you've seen something?}
<C>__{lisa}
<D>__{remember i said i saw a little girl roaming the hallways here? i know who she is. she's one of the defeo children who were killed. you ever seen her?}
<C>__{delaney}
<D>__{no.}
