<D>__{it's something i've been thinking about. how can evil exist in a world that many people believe was created by a loving god?}
<C>__{delaney}
<D>__{i don't believe that god is a bearded man who lives in the sky. or that the devil is a red demon with horns. i believe god and satan are within all of us. god is our human side. satan is our animal side. whether we become good or evil depends which side of us we feed.}
<C>__{lisa}
<D>__{it's a frightening thing to believe that if god exists he is not powerful enough to stop evil.}
